  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8109367">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8109367/" class="title-link">“诗三百，一言以蔽之，思无邪”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8109367"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u42033941-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">公益霎哈嘉瑜伽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-10-01"
      class="main-meta">2016-10-01 12:45:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8109367_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《诗经》是中国第一部诗歌总集，收入自西周初年至春秋中叶大约五百多年的诗歌（前11世纪至前6世纪），又称《诗三百》。先秦称为《诗》。西汉时被尊为儒家经典，始称《诗经》，并沿用至今。《诗经》（英译为：The Book of Songs）中最早的作品大约成于西周时期。全书主要收集了...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8109367_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8109367_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










